// qpf

// PSR-1    ///////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
 - <?php or <?= tags
 - UTF-8 sans BOM only
 - declarative or cause side-effects but not both
 - Namesspaces and classes must be autoloaded
 - class names in UpperCasesName
 - class constant in uppercase and underscore separator
 - method in camelCaseName

// PSR-2    ///////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
 - PSR-1 compliant
 - 4 spaces for tabs
 - no hard limit on line length but 120 to 80 recommended
 - 1 blank line after the namespace declaration
 - 1 blank line after the use declaration
 - opening braces on next line for class and function declaration
 - visibility (private,protected,public) mandatory
 - placement : abstract|final private|protected|public static
 - 1 space after control structure (if,elseif,else,switch)
 - no space after function or method
 - opening brace on the same line
 - no space after parenthesis crontrol structure and no space before closing
 
// PSR-3   ///////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
  - logger interface
  
// one word reserved classname   -->     get_declared_classes ()
 
 - Closure
 - Directory
 - Exception
 - Generator
 - Iterator
 - Phar
 - Reflection
 - Serializable
 - Traversable
 - Throwable
 
 